title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre willing to push your limits to help out a partner or close ally today. You may sacrifice a fair amount of time to take care of a dear one. Although they might lack appreciation for your efforts, youre not putting so much on the line because you think you deserve a gold star and a cookie. You do what you must because you value your connection and want to be of service. But remember to save some quiet time to replenish your energy. You cant help anyone if you exhaust your resources. Dont just be good to others, be good to yourself, too. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
